<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head lang="en">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>绿色喜墅-案例展示</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,user-scalable=0"/>
    <meta name="keywords" content="关键词，tapas"/>
    <meta name="description" content="摘要，tapas"/>
    <script src="/js/jquery-1.8.3.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/js/jquery.SuperSlide.2.1.1.js"></script>
    <link href="/css/css.css" type="text/css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/keyframes.css" type="text/css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(document).ready(function(){
            $(".prev,.next").hover(function(){
                $(this).stop(true,false).fadeTo("show",0.9);
            },function(){
                $(this).stop(true,false).fadeTo("show",0.4);
            });
            $(".banner-box").slide({
                titCell:".hd ul",
                mainCell:".bd ul",
                effect:"fold",
                interTime:3500,
                delayTime:500,
                autoPlay:true,
                autoPage:true,
                trigger:"click"
            });
            $(".btn_top").click(function(){
                $("html,body").animate({scrollTop:'0'},400);return false;
            });
            $(".btn_top").click(function(){
                $("html,body").animate({scrollTop:'0'},400);
                return false;
            });
            $(".coll_detail_pic").hover(function(){
                $(this).find(".bg_big").show();
            },function(){
                $(this).find(".bg_big").hide();
            });
            $(".bg_big").click(function(){
                $(".pic_big").show();
                $(".bg").height($(window).height());
            });
            $(".icon-close").click(function(){
                $(".pic_big").hide();
            });
            $(".bg").click(function(){
                $(".pic_big").hide();
            });
        });
    </script>
</head>
<body>
{{>header}}
        <div class="crumbs">
            <ul class="ie_maiDiv crumbs_list">
                <li>
                    <i class="icon-home"></i>
                    首页
                </li>
                <li>
                    <i class="icon-arrow-left"></i>
                    <i class="icon-camera_fill"></i>
                    案例展示
                </li>
            </ul>
            <div class="clear"> </div>
        </div>
        <!--面包屑-->
        <div class="mai_content">
            <div class="ie_maiDiv">
                <h2 class="in_title">
                <span class="icon-ye">

                </span>
                    案例展示
                <span class="icon-ye2">

                </span>
                </h2>
                <p class="in_about">公司所有设计师均有20年以上工作经历，资质深厚。 17年风雨历程，不仅造就了一代艰苦创业 、成就辉煌</p>

                <ul class="coll_tab">
                    <li {{#type_1}}class="active"{{/type_1}}>
                        <a href="/cases?type=1">家装案例</a>
                    </li>
                    <li {{#type_2}}class="active"{{/type_2}}>
                        <a href="/cases?type=2">工装案例</a>
                    </li>
                    <li {{#type_3}}class="active"{{/type_3}}>
                        <a href="/cases?type=3">商业案例</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <div class="coll_list">
                    {{#cases}}
                    <div class="coll_field_content">
                        <a class="coll_field_content_pic" href="/cases/1">
                            <img src="../images/pro_img.png" width="303" height="202"/>
                        </a>
                        <h3 class="coll_field_content_title">
                            <a href="/cases/1">
                                上海华侨城纯水岸
                            </a>
                            <span class="coll_field_content_title_txt">
                                现代简约风格
                            </span>
                        </h3>
                        <span class="icon-price">
                            160㎡
                        </span>
                        <div class="pull_right">
                            <a href="/cases/1">
                                <i class="icon-eye"></i>
                                查看设计
                            </a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="clear"></div>
                    </div>
                    {{/cases}}


                    {{>page}}

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!--content end-->

{{>footer}}
</body>
</html>